N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 12 ยง 65.56 - Submission without hearing or appearance

State Regulations

With leave of the Board, any proceeding where sufficient
facts have been admitted, stipulated, or otherwise included in the record may
be submitted at any time for decision or other appropriate action upon consent
of all parties. Notes
